{"tid":433691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【前解放軍居港屢犯案　甫出獄即爆竊今認罪】","createTime":"2017-10-12T14:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T07:57:20.000Z","uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"260f311873d02a1d097d98fe52a100fc9638ea39","tid":433691,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"曾於中國任解放軍及公安的男子朱書龍，移居香港後犯案纍纍，2016年7月時獲釋，甫出獄即再犯案，先到屯門一處工廈爆竊，繼而在全港各區犯案。<br />\n<br />\n朱書龍今日（10月12日）於灣仔區域法院認罪，還柙至10月30日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n62歲的前解放軍朱書龍，被控爆竊及外出時身藏爆竊工具等7項罪名。案發於2016年7月9日至8月18日期間，案發地點包括屯門、新蒲崗、荃灣及柴灣，在柴灣發達中心，被告連環爆竊3個單位，他離開前將部份爆竊工具藏於其中一單位的天花上，同晚外出時被警方截獲拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-12-2017/41976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-12-2017%2F41976&d=3af2D%2Flz%2F1Ki%2Br%2FNG%2Fkyiozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=af389c6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-12-2017/41976</a>"},{"pid":"96826725e223b02da6cc06e7601dec922178f548","tid":433691,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"休班警d friend 喎"},{"pid":"660466b52840608aeb90507fba7e6969ef91eca7","tid":433691,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbfc354e4ff0772f1912806aad17e8b84f30695","tid":433691,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"係咪解放軍喺灣仔玩汽油彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9236dae4effb18a1661c62059cd65450d9b22c46","tid":433691,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96826725e223b02da6cc06e7601dec922178f548","tid":433691,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"休班警d friend 喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"支那軍隊"},{"pid":"49c6a1